title: LP INVESTMENTS: How many tokens?
body:
How many tokens do you think we should use for invest in LP?

Tokens will be send to LP investments address, and a smart contract owner of this address will implement the investment strategy.

Note: the more tokens the LP investments address has, the more tokens it will receive per reflection in each transaction.
author: 0x05078E63d080c292478504Df1170289B23E9659B
